        biasedEnergyDiff net x i = biasedEnergy net (biasedUpdateState net x i) - biasedEnergy net x := rfl
        _ = biasedEnergy net x - biasedEnergy net x := by rw [h₁]
        _ = 0 := by ring
    exact h₂
``` 

